text: A.C. Maceratese is a football club in Italy. A.C. Maceratese plays in the D league. Their stadium is called Stadio Helvia Racina. It can hold 5,846 people. The chairman is named Massimo Paci. The manager is named Francesco Nocera. He makes most of the important decisions on the team. == References == Category:Italian football clubs Category:1922 establishments in Italy Category:Province of Macerata
